relevant_findings.heent: Non-conjunctival, extraocular movements intact, anicteric, moist mucous membranes.
relevant_findings.chest: Bilateral air entry, no wheezing, crackles, or ronchi.
relevant_findings.heart: S1 and S2 normal, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops.
relevant_findings.abdomen: Bowel sounds present, soft, mild epigastric tenderness to deep palpation, no guarding or rebound.
relevant_findings.extremities: No cyanosis, clubbing, or edema, 2+ pulses.
relevant_findings.neurological: Alert and oriented times three, cranial nerves II-XII intact.
